Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.player.Player

  • public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
    creates a player defining all its parameters like color, a boolean value based on its role(first player or not) its weapons, its powerups, its starting block, the gameboard of its starting block, the actions, teh gamecontroller of the player teh connection , teh damages (players that are damaged froom that player, and specific round
